title: Early tests show 'chemical weapon' substance used on Kim
text:
More 
Preliminary analysis from the Malaysian Chemistry Department has revealed the chemical substance used in the murder of Kim Jong-nam, the estranged half-brother of North Korean leader Kim Jong-un. 
"The Royal Malaysian Police has received the preliminary report from the Chemistry Department of Malaysia, with regards to the death of a North Korean national recently."
